'''IMFI''' is an acronym for '''I'''nitial, '''M'''edial, '''F'''inal, '''I'''solated, a [[writing system]] in which each character has four different potential shapes:
* ''initial'' - used for the first character in a word * ''medial'' - used in the middle of a word * ''final'' - used for the last character in a word * ''isolated'' - used for single-letter words
The [[Arabic]] and [[Syriac script]] is an example of an IMFI writing system.
